entry.database_comments: Sample Preparation: Prepared by using a freeze-drying method. Aqueous solutions of ''V2 O5'' and ''Nb2 O5'' in oxalic acid were frozen to liquid nitrogen temperature and then dried in vacuum chamber. The sample was then heated to 623 K for 30 minutes before the final heat treatment of 1273 K for 5 hours.
